<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="point-out">point out</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>把…指出来 (给看)；指出；指明：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>pointed out to</strong> him where I used to live.
我把我过去住的地方指给他看。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>pointed out that</strong> the road was not safe in winter.
他指出这条路冬天不安全。</p></div></div>